title._content: Russian Orlan spacesuit underwater spacewalk simulation

description._content: Collection: NASA Human Spaceflight Collection General Description: International Space Station Imagery Description: JSC2006-E-33957 (July 2006) --- Attired in a Russian Orlan spacesuit, astronaut Michael E. Lopez-Alegria, Expedition 14 commander and NASA space station science officer, participates in an underwater spacewalk simulation in the Hydrolab facility at the Gagarin Cosmonaut Training Center in Star City, Russia. SCUBA-equipped divers are in the water to assist the crewmembers in their rehearsal, intended to help prepare them for work on the exterior of the station. image id: Photo-jsc2006e33957 UID: SPD-SPFLT-Photo-jsc2 006e33957 original url: spaceflight.nasa.gov/gallery/images/station/crew-14/html/...
